sourcesContent: import { Typography } from '@material-ui/core' import GridContainer from 'components/Grid/GridContainer' import GridItem from 'components/Grid/GridItem' import ViewInfoActionModal from 'components/ReactTableActions/ViewInfo/ViewInfoActionModal' const ViewFestivosInfoModal = ({ viewInfo, closeViewInfoModal, info }) => { const { id_calendario, dia, mes, anio } = info return ( ID: {id_calendario} Día: {dia} Mes: {mes} Año: {anio} } /> ) } export default ViewFestivosInfoModal
